![Alt text](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/9GWSyFwu/images/4338e0e366f15e3ce83ce8ba2adf9045a2d85cf1.png)

In this resource pack you get more 100 totems of MineStack players.
IIt is recommended to download the latest version to use pack max.

 **To get the player's totem, you need to change the totem to the nickname of the players on the anvil.**

## Compatibility with the resource pack:

| Version             | Mods               | Result              |
|:---------------------:|:---------------------:|:---------------------:|
| Vanilla            | -              | ❌             |
| [Forge](<https://files.minecraftforge.net/net/minecraftforge/forge/> 'HELLO,')            | [Optifine](<https://optifine.net/downloads> 'I')              | ✅             |
| [Fabric](<https://fabricmc.net/use/installer/> 'NOT')            | [CIT Resewn](<https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-resewn/versions>  'MURKA!')              | ✅             |

